  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a randomized and comparative prospective test, monocentric and controlled (mirror
      therapy versus bimanual rehabilitation exercises), in single-blind (investigator and
      occupational therapist &quot; 1 &quot; do not know the type of rehabilitation performed).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
